12:54.005 --> 12:55.406
- Pick it up?
- Pick it up.

12:55.473 --> 12:56.674
Yeah.
Pick it up. Try it.

12:56.742 --> 12:58.009
- I'll pick it up.

12:58.076 --> 12:59.343
- You're a big guy.
