21:18.242 --> 21:20.645
<i>they booed me off the stage.</i>
[booing]

21:20.712 --> 21:22.246
<i>I was devastated.</i>

21:22.314 --> 21:24.415
<i>I threw my props in the trash,</i>

21:24.417 --> 21:26.617
<i>but I realized I had the power</i>

21:26.685 --> 21:29.386
<i>to turn that "no"
into a "yes."</i>

21:29.454 --> 21:32.189
<i>Next, I set my mind
to performing</i>

