The remaining cards
are gonna sit this game out.

23:14.994 --> 23:17.094
Now, Alyson,
I need two decks of cards.

23:17.161 --> 23:21.365
That blue deck
and this red deck of cards,

23:21.432 --> 23:24.435
also known as the mystery deck.

23:24.437 --> 23:27.371
And you might ask why.

