- Why?
- Here's why, Alyson.

23:29.842 --> 23:31.375
- One of the red cards

23:31.410 --> 23:34.578
is facing
in the opposite direction.

23:34.613 --> 23:38.315
It is the mystery card.

23:38.382 --> 23:39.516
Both: Ooh.

23:39.584 --> 23:41.418
- All right. We're gonna try
that part again.

23:41.420 --> 23:43.187
- Okay.
- One of the red cards

23:43.254 --> 23:45.522
is facing
in the opposite direction.

23:45.590 --> 23:48.525
It is the mystery card.

23:48.593 --> 23:49.994
- Ooh.
- Good. Good.

