is easy to get into.

39:12.616 --> 39:14.717
Some say heaven
is hard to get into.

39:14.785 --> 39:18.588
Some say heaven is a place
on Earth, and they're right.

39:18.655 --> 39:20.323
It's right here.
That's heaven,

39:20.390 --> 39:23.292
and picture anything you want
for heaven in there.

39:23.360 --> 39:27.163
Maybe it's angels
on fluffy clouds with wings

39:27.230 --> 39:28.832
and halos playing harps.

39:28.899 --> 39:30.800
Or maybe it's my kind of heaven,

39:30.802 --> 39:33.970
which would be Sun Ra
playing Bob Dylan tunes

39:34.037 --> 39:37.707
while I eat vegan penuche fudge
and watch the Three Stooges

39:37.774 --> 39:41.878
chase a honey badger.
Now, when they said a needle

39:41.880 --> 39:44.547
they didn't mean
a modern, little needle.

39:44.615 --> 39:48.017
The Sumerian needle was
a Bedouin tentmaker's needle

39:48.019 --> 39:51.354
with a huge eye like this
for ropes to go through.

39:51.422 --> 39:55.358
And Teller will be playing
the part of the camel.

39:55.426 --> 39:57.761
[laughter]

39:59.963 --> 40:05.868
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:05.936 --> 40:09.238
He'll also be playing
the part of the rich man,

40:09.240 --> 40:11.374
which he was, until 2020.

40:11.376 --> 40:13.342
Cover that. Come on.
Get that tape on there.

40:13.410 --> 40:16.045
Spin it around.
Get the tape all over there.

40:16.112 --> 40:19.516
It is impossible
to get into heaven there,

40:19.583 --> 40:23.319
so we're gonna show
that they are not unequal.

40:23.386 --> 40:25.354
That it is not more difficult

40:25.422 --> 40:26.689
for a rich man to go into heaven

40:26.756 --> 40:28.858
than for a camel
through the eye of the needle.

40:28.860 --> 40:31.461
They're gonna put it up
on this stand here,

40:31.528 --> 40:33.129
and then, if you would please,
Zeke,

40:33.131 --> 40:38.334
affix this needle
to the front of the box there.

40:38.336 --> 40:42.605
And cut a hole into heaven
right there.

40:42.607 --> 40:46.542
Here's the original New
Testament Sumerian text here.

40:46.610 --> 40:51.080
We have the rich man
into the kingdom of heaven

40:51.147 --> 40:55.017
not equal to the camel
through the eye of the needle.

40:55.019 --> 40:56.819
Our beef is with this symbol
right here.

40:56.887 --> 40:58.955
We think they are exactly equal,

40:59.022 --> 41:03.259
and we can prove it.
We have heaven over there.

41:03.326 --> 41:06.463
We have the needle there,
and we have our camel,

41:06.497 --> 41:08.231
and we have our rich man.

41:08.233 --> 41:10.967
We have our camel
and our rich man.

41:11.034 --> 41:12.101
We have our camel.

41:12.136 --> 41:15.438
Now, the camel has to get
all four hooves

41:15.506 --> 41:18.741
and both humps--it's
a dromedary--into the needle,

41:18.808 --> 41:20.777
at the same time

41:20.844 --> 41:27.450
that the rich man goes into
the kingdom of heaven.

41:27.452 --> 41:29.719
I think we made our point.

41:29.786 --> 41:32.489
Exactly equal.
